 967:Drivers/lvgl/src/widgets/buttonmatrix/lv_buttonmatrix.c **** /**
 968:Drivers/lvgl/src/widgets/buttonmatrix/lv_buttonmatrix.c ****  * Enforces a single button being toggled on the button matrix.
 969:Drivers/lvgl/src/widgets/buttonmatrix/lv_buttonmatrix.c ****  * It simply clears the toggle flag on other buttons.
 970:Drivers/lvgl/src/widgets/buttonmatrix/lv_buttonmatrix.c ****  * @param obj Button matrix object
